  "body": "### Added\r\n- Support for LOAD KEY command (INS=0x82) to load authentication keys into reader memory\r\n- Support for GENERAL AUTHENTICATE command (INS=0x86) for MIFARE Classic authentication\r\n- Dependency `keyple-util-java-lib:2.4.1`\r\n### Upgraded\r\n- `keyple-plugin-storagecard-java-api` from `1.0.0` to `1.1.0`\r\n- `slf4j-api` from `1.7.32` to `1.7.36` (compileOnly) "
